### ============================================================
### 账户管理接口
### ============================================================

### 变量定义
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken =


### 获取账户列表及 Token 统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/account
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### 刷新账户凭据
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/account/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### 测试账户连通性
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/account/test
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### 启动账户引导 (OAuth) — method 可选: qrcode / browser
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/account/bootstrap
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "qrcode",
  "region": "china"
}


### 启动账户引导 (浏览器方式, 国际区)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/account/bootstrap
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "browser",
  "region": "international"
}


### 查询引导状态 (替换为实际 session ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/account/bootstrap/status?session=your-session-id
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### 提交引导结果 (替换为实际 session ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/account/bootstrap/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session": "your-session-id"
}

### 添加 CodeBuddy 账号 (access_token 必填)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/account
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "codebuddy",
  "enabled": true,
  "label": "my-codebuddy-account",
  "auth": {
    "access_token": "ck_fn7vyognuv40.qOxGvXMBn9rjfZo1lz19JbJzbfFCWxoErTD8X1rcEfQ"
  }
}


### 添加 CodeBuddy 账号 (仅 access_token, 最简写法)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/account
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "codebuddy",
  "enabled": true,
  "auth": {
    "access_token": "your-codebuddy-access-token"
  }
}
